## **7ï¸âƒ£ S3 Advanced Features**  

âœ… **S3 Versioning** â€“ Keeps multiple versions of files (prevents accidental deletion).  
âœ… **S3 Lifecycle Policies** â€“ Automatically moves objects between storage classes.  
âœ… **S3 Replication** â€“ Replicates data across different AWS regions.  
âœ… **S3 Event Notifications** â€“ Triggers Lambda functions when an object is added/deleted.  
âœ… **S3 Transfer Acceleration** â€“ Faster uploads using AWS Edge Locations.  

