ğŸ“Œ **Website Hosting** â€“ Store static websites (HTML, CSS, JS).  
ğŸ“Œ **Backup & Restore** â€“ Store backups securely in S3.  
ğŸ“Œ **Big Data & Analytics** â€“ Store and process large datasets.  
ğŸ“Œ **Data Archiving** â€“ Move old data to S3 Glacier to save costs.  
ğŸ“Œ **Content Distribution** â€“ Deliver media files, videos, and images via CloudFront.  

